{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were standing with four machine guns, shooting down to the graves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I would say most of them was alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They took like a-- a special chemical-like, it looked like a paint.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They spilled over, the bodies shouldn't smell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After, the ground was still lifting up, was very little ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's why they were using it as garbage to dump.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because half of them, the bones, of course, are still there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because I saw with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was kissing the bones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My son kept on crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I was crying, I said, I kissing my parents bones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So what happened there, I saw what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I start running again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They shot me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And in front of the-- it's like from here to the lobby, that's all-- there's a ditch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Surprisingly, there's still some water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "When I went with my two beautiful children, [SOBBING] when I saw that ditch, I laid down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They couldn't get me off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[SOBBING] It reminded, the way I was standing, I was shot with [INAUDIBLE] was somebody getting killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After that, it took-- it took about two hours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It quiet down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I lift up my head all the way-- [SIGHS] [SOBBING] was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I came out to the grave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I looked in it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was debating if I should lay down and die there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[SOBBING] Something happened to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I figured to myself, no, life go to go on-- [SOBS] I'm sorry-- I start walking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] I walk about a half a mile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw two boys walking there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One is holding eye like that with some of his-- part of his pants.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He lost his eye.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
